title: This TV Actress Just Got Hitched And Her Wedding Photos Are Beautiful | MissMalini
text:
Swagata Dam Feb . 24 . 2017 
Ishqbaaz actress Shireena Sambyal tied the knot with her beau Vishnu Rao on 15th February in Noida. And I came across some really gorgeous photos of their shaandaar shaadi on my friend and one of my favourite wedding photographer, Stuti Dasgupta ‘s page, The Cheesecake Project .
